  "detailed_description": "<strong><i>Peepo Hop!</i></strong> is a precision platformer that will test your challenge your skills. Play as Peepo to reclaim his treasure perched at the top but be careful one wrong hop can send Peepo falling back down.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533120/extras/2c0cb5af50113e1baba9c5b3aff95cfe.poster.avif?t=1705924669\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533120/extras/2c0cb5af50113e1baba9c5b3aff95cfe.webm?t=1705924669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533120/extras/2c0cb5af50113e1baba9c5b3aff95cfe.mp4?t=1705924669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Master the Art of Precision:</strong> Take control of the unique jumping mechanic, where you charge Peepo's left and right leg independently. Combine the strength of each leg to change the trajectory of your jump.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533120/extras/adf3b42d14bd2d832cd990816d739869.poster.avif?t=1705924669\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533120/extras/adf3b42d14bd2d832cd990816d739869.webm?t=1705924669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533120/extras/adf3b42d14bd2d832cd990816d739869.mp4?t=1705924669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Race to the Top:</strong> Finish your ascent and your time will be recorded on the leaderboard. Contribute your time to a group on the leaderboard where the average time of your group is ranked amongst other groups.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533120/extras/4204943e4d2109833dfdf82161198dd7.poster.avif?t=1705924669\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533120/extras/4204943e4d2109833dfdf82161198dd7.webm?t=1705924669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533120/extras/4204943e4d2109833dfdf82161198dd7.mp4?t=1705924669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><i><u>Peepo needs your help to reclaim his treasure. Mind your hops and aim for the top. Try not to fall too many times. Good luck!</u></i></strong>",
